if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2654ec6badc84e4cab2e5c50650e0095396a3e8","tid":150291,"uid":47411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T02:50:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔拍你會唔會後悔？<br />\n我都明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 試過真係好鍾意一個人，明知唔會有結果同會好 hurt都繼續落去，因為唔捨得佢同埋想對佢好</blockquote><br />\n我會後悔 但係我想追求穩定幸福多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢覺得自己未玩夠 我愈對佢好佢愈內疚"},{"pid":"3a0c0e02bf21ce792d88e0c26a31b1249d5701be","tid":150291,"uid":47411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T02:54:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔拍你會唔會後悔？<br />\n我都明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 試過真係好鍾意一個人，明知唔會有結果同會好 hurt都繼續落去，因為唔捨得佢同埋想對佢好</blockquote><br />\n話唔定 你地一齊左 佢會改變主意？因爲開始對你有感情 到時就唔捨得分手？ 我都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢未同我一齊已經驚自己同我行唔遠 咁一齊咗咪仲多野諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我問過佢 除左專一 其他嘢我都可以唔要 佢話就係因為佢做唔到呢樣嘢所以想放我走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"403f3f084739501c5362edb0bd77a532f6b45279","tid":150291,"uid":83531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T03:08:41.000Z","msg":"佢都講到咁 離場好啲<br />\n去馬盞搞到2面都傷"},{"pid":"66aea325a99ab8ce587d4bd028cf5a5e0c970e0c","tid":150291,"uid":20842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T03:09:43.000Z","msg":"你咁問似想去馬<br />\n受唔到刺激就離場"},{"pid":"05b0baa65390c245fee99ec374086f3a39d3aa20","tid":150291,"uid":47411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T03:21:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢都講到咁 離場好啲<br />\n去馬盞搞到2面都傷</blockquote><br />\n已經傷曬 之前我同佢除左身分之外平時同情侶無異"},{"pid":"62dab7f3e73a383872f537c95d78debd3bd7445e","tid":150291,"uid":47411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T03:22:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你咁問似想去馬<br />\n受唔到刺激就離場</blockquote><br />\n想離但係唔捨得 想去又會介意<img src=\"/assets